<h1>Directory of Consumer Information Resources</h1>

    <p>
        <a href="/">Home</a> >
            <a href="/Home">Home</a>  >             <a href="/Home/Consumer_Information">Consumer Information</a>         </p>

<p><p>This category provides product and service information so that consumers can make informed purchasing decisions. It also provides information about service contracts, warranties, recalls, and other product or service information for consumers who already have made purchases. </p><p>Sites in this category are buyers' guides, decision guides, price comparisons, recall information, or tips and advice. </p> Sites which are primarily promotional in nature, and not significantly useful in making informed shopping choices, can be found in appropriate Business, Regional, or Shopping categories.</p>

