<h2>Resources in This Category</h2>
<ul>

    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.beststuff.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>BestStuff.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.beststuff.com/</strong></font> <br /> A network of reporters, authors, and industry experts offering reviews of new products.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.consumerhandbook.ca/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Canadian Consumer Handbook</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.consumerhandbook.ca/</strong></font> <br /> Offers information that includes online shopping, contracts, housing and home renovations, identity theft and collection agencies. Created and updated by the Consumer Measures Committee. [English and French]</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.consumerinformation.ca/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Canadian Consumer Information</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.consumerinformation.ca/</strong></font> <br /> Consumer information guides covering a variety of topics including children, consumer products and services, environment, food, health, housing and finance.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.checkbook.org/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Consumers' Checkbook</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.checkbook.org/</strong></font> <br /> This independent, non-profit consumer authority provides articles and ratings for local services in the United States.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.consumersearch.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>ConsumerSearch.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.consumersearch.com/</strong></font> <br /> Database of categorized consumer product reviews from a variety of news and trade publications. For each product, it ranks and describes all reviews, provides a full story of expert analysis, and lists top rated products by category.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://couponshowto.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Coupons How-To</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://couponshowto.com/</strong></font> <br /> A guide to using coupons with articles on money-saving tips, tutorials and videos.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.econsumer.gov/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>EConsumer.gov</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.econsumer.gov/</strong></font> <br /> Provides information on consumer protection laws in thirteen countries and offers consumers a way to file complaints online.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.nrcan.gc.ca/energy/products/energuide/12523" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>EnerGuide</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.nrcan.gc.ca/energy/products/energuide/12523</strong></font> <br /> Produced by the Canadian government&#039;s Office of Energy Efficiency, rates home appliances for cost of operation and gives tips and advice.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://usafact.org/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Federation of American Consumers and Travelers (FACT)</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://usafact.org/</strong></font> <br /> A national consumer organization offering benefits, discounts, and programs for consumers and travelers. Offers subscription based articles on cost saving health care benefits, scholarships, grants, and non-partisan political reports.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.fixya.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Fixya.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.fixya.com/</strong></font> <br /> Support information for consumer electronics and appliances, repair services, manuals, guides, faqs and troubleshooting.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.infofaq.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>InfoFAQ</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.infofaq.com/</strong></font> <br /> Questions and answers about buying products and services over the Internet.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.instruction-manuals.co.uk/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Instruction Manuals UK</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.instruction-manuals.co.uk/</strong></font> <br /> Instruction manuals for products sold in the United Kingdom.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.instructionsheets.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>InstructionSheets.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.instructionsheets.com/</strong></font> <br /> Includes alphabetical list of manufacturers with links to their sites and list of product instruction manuals offered for download.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.jdpower.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>JD Power Information Center</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.jdpower.com/</strong></font> <br /> Using consumer satisfaction data collected, this site provides consumers information to help them in their buying decisions.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.manualsonline.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>ManualsOnline.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.manualsonline.com/</strong></font> <br /> Contains free instruction manuals and other support documents including operator and user guides, and how-to information for all sorts of appliances, machines and devices.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.myprimetime.com/misc/me_meters.shtml" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Master Me Meter</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.myprimetime.com/misc/me_meters.shtml</strong></font> <br /> Life calculators and tools for career, family, and work.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://www.mouthshut.com/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>MouthShut.com</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://www.mouthshut.com/</strong></font> <br /> Consumers research, compare, and review products and services.</p>
    </li>	
    <li class="listings">
    <h4><a href="http://publications.usa.gov/" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none"><strong>Publications.usa.gov</strong></a></h4>
	<p><font color="#013C7F"><strong>http://publications.usa.gov/</strong></font> <br /> Provides a library of consumer interest publications on a variety of topics. A service of the U.S. General Services Administration.</p>
    </li>	
</ul>

